Akosua Dansoa is a beautiful and curvy lady who has suddenly become an internet sensation after she documented how she helps her mother in selling farm produce in her locality. Her mother is a petty trader who sells cocoayam, cassava, plantain and other food items on social media. The humble dark-skinned lady has come in handy in the area of relieving her mother of the stress of working overtime at her shop. This has helped the mom in making more sales to her delight. She is being celebrated in her home-country Ghana for not venturing into prostitution like some ladies of her age do to augment their income. See more images below: Source